{"name":"Incidents","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"Deepnight Revelation Book 3, pg. 25","results":[{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"zLYJRrvIXGeDZTAk","text":"Something goes sufficiently badly wrong that the Incident becomes a Mishap.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"bxpEHmTO3rnOssNw","text":"An equipment breakdown causes difficulties for the detachment or crew. For example, the main sensor processing centre suffers a software glitch and has to be rebooted whilst the ship is trying to scan local traffic. The Travellers will have to figure a way around the problem, which cannot be fixed in time to complete the task at hand.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"8E6KaJn4VOeIaBBC","text":"A discipline problem occurs during the operation, disrupting the work of everyone involved. A heavy handed solution might cause further resentment but letting crewmembers get away with indiscipline will lead to more problems in the future.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"otyVeBxxjcWSiXrt","text":"The operation is made more complex by changing circumstances. This will usually be something more inconvenient than deadly, such as equipment malfunction, unexpected environmental change, or some other source of unnecessary delay and difficulty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"jM7YNPpc7VLA5at6","text":"Some of the necessary equipment is unexpectedly missing, offline or out of commission, requiring a creative workaround or hurried fix.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"Uw6Lxtq16hLbZ82D","text":"A minor hiccup occurs, such as an infraction of regulations that requires a hearing and disciplinary action. This might be embarrassing in front of outsiders and could have repercussions if the crew are discontent.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"qGbYSRpOsDgaRSo5","text":"Something unusual is spotted; a sensor blip, an intriguing arrangement of planets and other bodies in the system, strange atmospheric composition or something equally puzzling but not immediately threatening.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"jx2TYjysJYATzU3h","text":"A crewmember or detachment demonstrates unexpected resourcefulness and gets the job done better and quicker than expected.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"SeBQvOW2CulJ82NE","text":"A typically uncooperative crewmember pitches in with a will and is helpful in completing the task. The reason for this change of heart is not immediately obvious.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"9xeSDwt2uwy2I9BW","text":"The task requires dusting off an unusual piece of equipment or trying out a technique not normally used. Make a Difficult (10+) check using CEI and if successful, gain MOR +1.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"G0EqTEExRfwSV82W","text":"Things seem to go pretty well and in the middle of the task an Opportunity occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}}],"formula":"2d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"yeZEZ0XOw4URiaL8":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"twodsix","systemVersion":"2.32.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1694641978258,"modifiedTime":1694645251879,"lastModifiedBy":"yeZEZ0XOw4URiaL8"},"_id":"tz4CFQKUyIe7JBld"}
